0;25;0RUNdef pascaluv_trojuhelnik(n):\n    value = 1\n    for i in range(1, n + 1):\n        value *= i\n    return value\n\ndef binomial_coefficient(n, k):\n    return factorial(n) / (factorial(n - k) * factorial(k))\n\ndef pascal_binomial(n):\n
